src.zip_lookup.utils package¶

Submodules¶

src.zip_lookup.utils.global_variable module¶

Global variable for this project.

This module contains the global variable for this project. Specifically, the API Key, Email and Password of the Zip API. The URL of this API: https://zipapi.us.

src.zip_lookup.utils.global_variable.API_KEY¶

The API Key will be used when making requests to the Zip API.

Type

str

src.zip_lookup.utils.global_variable.EMAIL¶

The Email address that used to authenticate with the Zip API when making requests.

Type

str

src.zip_lookup.utils.global_variable.PASSWORD¶

The password that will be used to authenticate

Type

str

when making requests to the Zip API.
